[4.6943, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[J\u001b[0;7m\u000f West of House                                                                                                                    Score: 0        Moves: 0      \u001b[31;1H\u001b[m\u000fZORK I: The Great Underground Empire\r\u001b[32d"]
[4.694425, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The game Zork has started, and the player is currently at the starting location, West of House. The objective is to navigate through the game and reach the end with the maximum possible score.\",\"explanation\":\"The initial steps in Zork often involve exploring the immediate surroundings to acquire useful items or gain more information. We will interact with the mailbox first.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"open mailbox\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[4.694425, "o", "Copyright (c) 1981, 1982, 1983 Infocom, Inc. All rights reserved.\r\u001b[33dZORK is a registered trademark of Infocom, Inc.\r\u001b[34dRevision 88 / Serial number 840726\r\u001b[36dWest of House\r\u001b[37dYou are standing in an open field west of a white house, with a boarded front door.\r\u001b[38dThere is a small mailbox here.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[6.402509, "i", "open mailbox\n"]
[6.402966, "o", "open"]
[6.403036, "o", " mailb"]
[6.403116, "o", "ox"]
[6.403298, "o", "\r\u001b[2d\u001b[3M\u001bM\u001b[154G"]
[6.403539, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The mailbox is open, revealing a leaflet inside. This is a typical first step in Zork to gather information.\",\"explanation\":\"The next logical step is to read the leaflet to gather information that might be useful for the adventure.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"read leaflet\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[6.403539, "o", "\u001b[0;7m\u000f1\r\u001b[38d\u001b[m\u000fOpening the small mailbox reveals a leaflet.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[7.797609, "i", "read leaflet\n"]
[7.798078, "o", "read leaflet"]
[7.79837, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The leaflet has been read, providing an introductory message about the adventure in Zork. There's no further actionable information from the leaflet itself.\",\"explanation\":\"The next logical step is to explore the surroundings by moving around. Since the front door of the house is boarded, an alternative entrance should be sought.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"north\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[7.79837, "o", "\r\u001b[2d\u001b[8M\u001bM\u001b[154G\u001b[0;7m\u000f2\r\u001b[33d\u001b[m\u000f(Taken)\r\u001b[34d\"WELCOME TO ZORK!\r\u001b[36dZORK is a game of adventure, danger, and low cunning. In it you will explore some of the most amazing territory ever seen by mortals. No computer should be\r\u001b[37dwithout one!\"\r\u001b[40d>"]
[9.577386, "i", "north\n"]
[9.57781, "o", "no"]
[9.578012, "o", "rth"]
[9.57809, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The player is now at the north side of the house, where there are no doors and the windows are boarded. There is an option to follow a narrow path to the north through the trees.\",\"explanation\":\"Since the house cannot be entered from the north side, the next step is to explore the narrow path to the north to potentially find an alternate entrance or useful items.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"north\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[9.57809, "o", "\r\u001b[2d\u001b[4M\u001bM\u001b[C\u001b[0;7m\u000fNorth of House\u001b[154G3\r\u001b[37d\u001b[m\u000fNorth of House\r\u001b[38dYou are facing the north side of a white house. There is no door here, and all the windows are boarded up. To the north a narrow path winds through the trees.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[11.784487, "i", "north\n"]
[11.785693, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The player is now on a forest path that is dimly lit, with the path continuing to the north and south. There is a large tree with low branches nearby.\",\"explanation\":\"The next step is to explore the large tree to see if it has any items or routes of interest, such as climbing it for a better view or finding an object.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"climb tree\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[11.785693, "o", "north\r\u001b[2d\u001b[5M\u001bM\u001b[C\u001b[0;7m\u000fForest Path   \u001b[154G4\r\u001b[36d\u001b[m\u000fForest Path\r\u001b[37dThis is a path winding through a dimly lit forest. The path heads north-south here. One particularly large tree with some low branches stands at the edge of the\u001b[38;1Hpath.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[13.515135, "i", "climb tree\n"]
[13.516096, "o", "climb tree"]
[13.516319, "o", "\r\u001b[2d"]
[13.516471, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The player is now up a tree, next to a bird's nest containing a large, jeweled egg. The egg is fragile, hinged, and clasped, indicating it may open to reveal something inside.\",\"explanation\":\"The next action is to take the egg, as it might be valuable or contain something useful for the adventure.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"take egg\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[13.516471, "o", "\u001b[9M\u001bM\u001b[C\u001b[0;7m\u000fUp a Tree  \u001b[154G5\r\u001b[32d\u001b[m\u000fUp a Tree\r\u001b[33dYou are about 10 feet above the ground nestled among some large branches. The nearest branch above you is above your reach.\r\u001b[34dBeside you on the branch is a small bird's nest.\r\u001b[35dIn the bird's nest is a large egg encrusted with precious jewels, apparently scavenged by a childless songbird. The egg is covered with fine gold inlay, and\r\u001b[36dornamented in lapis lazuli and mother-of-pearl. Unlike most eggs, this one is hinged and closed with a delicate looking clasp. The egg appears extremely\r\u001b[37dfragile.\r\u001b[38dYou hear in the distance the chirping of a song bird.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[15.381811, "i", "take egg\n"]
[15.382576, "o", "take egg\r\u001b[2d\u001b[3M\u001b[1;138H\u001b[0;7m\u000f5\u001b[154G"]
[15.382704, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The player successfully took the jeweled egg from the bird's nest. This action increased the score, indicating progress in the game.\",\"explanation\":\"Descend from the tree to continue exploring the game world. The goal is to find and collect more valuable items, or to find ways to progress through the game, possibly finding an entrance into the house.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"down\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[15.382704, "o", "6\r\u001b[38d\u001b[m\u000fTaken.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[18.243196, "i", "down\n"]
[18.252929, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The player is back on the forest path, having successfully taken the jeweled egg from the tree. The path continues both north and south, offering further exploration opportunities.\",\"explanation\":\"Continue exploring the forest path to the north to discover new areas or potential items that might aid in the adventure.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"north\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[18.252929, "o", "down\r\u001b[2d\u001b[4M\u001bM\u001b[C\u001b[0;7m\u000fForest Path\u001b[154G7\r\u001b[37d\u001b[m\u000fForest Path\r\u001b[38dYou hear in the distance the chirping of a song bird.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[20.277748, "i", "north\n"]
[20.278872, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The player is now in a clearing surrounded by forest, with a path leading back south. There is a pile of leaves on the ground, which could potentially hide something useful.\",\"explanation\":\"Investigate the pile of leaves to see if there are any hidden items or paths beneath them.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"examine leaves\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[20.278872, "o", "north\r\u001b[2d\u001b[5M\u001bM\u001b[C\u001b[0;7m\u000fClearing   \u001b[154G8\r\u001b[36d\u001b[m\u000fClearing\r\u001b[37dYou are in a clearing, with a forest surrounding you on all sides. A path leads south.\r\u001b[38dOn the ground is a pile of leaves.\r\u001b[40d>"]
[21.945988, "i", "examine leaves\n"]
[21.949667, "m", "{\"state_analysis\":\"The pile of leaves in the clearing was examined but nothing special was found beneath them. The path leads back south, but no other immediate actions are apparent in the clearing.\",\"explanation\":\"Since the leaves yielded no result, the next step is to search the clearing more thoroughly to ensure no hidden items or entrances are missed.\",\"commands\":[{\"keystrokes\":\"search clearing\\n\",\"is_blocking\":false,\"timeout_sec\":5.0}],\"is_task_complete\":false}"]
[21.949667, "o", "examine leaves\r\u001b[2d\u001b[3M\u001bM\u001b[154G\u001b[0;7m\u000f9\r\u001b[38d\u001b[m\u000fThere's nothing special about the pile of leaves.\r\u001b[40d>"]
